1) install webpack globally
     npm install webpack -g
2) install webpack devserver globbaly
     npm install webpack-dev-server -g
3) creat package.json file in project
     npm init
4) add dependencies into package.json file
     devDependencies and dependencies
5) install dependencies
     npm install

*** Because wants to use webpack we need to create webpack config file on project root ***
6) create webpack.config.js in root
7) Test webpack
     webpack-dev-server
8) open  http://localhost:8080/app/ in browser
